Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.34,0:45:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瘋狂沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.10,0:45:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為真愛瘋狂沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.08,0:45:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你滲入我心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.98,0:45:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流經我身體每處
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.42,0:45:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我眼中的樂與愁
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.06,0:45:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的喜與憂
