Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.40,0:45:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何 我卻清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.39,0:46:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身著藏紅袍
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.59,0:46:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欲為高德修僧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.98,0:46:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我釋放眼中魔幻
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.30,0:46:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你忘卻磨難
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.96,0:46:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瘋狂沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.29,0:46:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是清涼晨露
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.38,0:46:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竊攜滿園芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.90,0:46:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如滔滔洪流
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.73,0:46:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開山斷石
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.47,0:46:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瘋狂沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.31,0:46:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為真愛瘋狂沉迷
